<table style="width:100%; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; border-collapse:collapse;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:24px; background-color:#0b3c70; color:#ffffff; text-align:center;">
      <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:22px;">Reset your Property UAE password</h1>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:24px; background-color:#ffffff; color:#1f2933;">
      <p>Hi {{recipientName}},</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset your Property UAE account password. Click the button below to choose a new password.</p>
      <p style="text-align:center; margin:32px 0;">
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="display:inline-block; background-color:#2563eb; color:#ffffff; padding:12px 24px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:4px; font-weight:bold;">
          Reset Password
        </a>
      </p>
      <p>This link will expire in {{expiresInMinutes}} minutes. If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email and your password will remain the same.</p>
      <p style="font-size:12px; color:#6b7280;">For your security, this link can only be used once.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:24px;">
        Regards,<br />
        Property UAE Team
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:12px 24px; background-color:#f2f7fb; color:#4f5d75; font-size:12px; text-align:center;">
      This message was sent from Property UAE (notifications@logixcontact.site)
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>


